oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Denny-Moeller Talent Agency Job No. 36443
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Wagoner, Porter; Jean, Norma;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1008) for an order placed by the Denny-Moeller Talent Agency for 100 two color window cards for a performance by Porter Wagoner, Norma Jean, and others at the Cunningham High School in Presque Isle, Maine for March 26. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
